      {
        "question": "Do I need to change the SASS file syntax (e.g., replace @import with @use)?",
        "answer": "Only if the new compiler reports errors. The migration itself does not require a blanket rewrite, but any files that use the deprecated @import syntax must be updated to @use/@forward to compile successfully."
